      • getDefault

        MetadataFieldMapper getDefault(Settings indexSettings,
                               MappedFieldType fieldType,
                               java.lang.String typeName)
        Get the default MetadataFieldMapper to use, if nothing had to be parsed.
        Parameters:
        fieldType - null if this is the first root mapper on this index, the existing fieldType for this index otherwise
        indexSettings - the index-level settings
        fieldType - the existing field type for this meta mapper on the current index or null if this is the first type being introduced
        typeName - the name of the type that this mapper will be used on
